title: Angels won't bring back Butcher, Baylor as coaches
text: Angels won't bring back Butcher, Baylor as coaches Wednesday, 14 October 2015 (3 minutes ago) The Los Angeles Angels will not bring back pitching coach Mike Butcher and hitting coach Don Baylor.New general manager Billy Eppler announced in a statement Tuesday night that the team would not renew the coaches' contracts.Butcher joined the Angels as pitching coach in 2006 and said in the team's statement that he'd talked at length with team president John Carpino and Eppler since the general manager's hiring last week.
